== Committer Learning Path

Podling committers are the backbone of community development.  
This path provides orientation for new committers to understand their role, responsibilities, and how to collaborate effectively within the Apache Incubator.

[.small]
*Key:* 📘 Guide 🖥️ Slide Deck 🎞️ Video 🧩 Quiz 🧠 Practice / Scenario

== Steps

1. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Committer+Onboarding[Podling Committer Onboarding] — what new committers need to know  
2. 🖥️ **Slide deck:** link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/committers/index.html[Committer Onboarding] — overview of expectations, ASF culture, and best practices  
3. 🎞️ **Watch:** link:https://youtu.be/JdKAeaDKk9k[Committer Onboarding] — video of Committer Onboarding presentation

